{"tid":239170,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"到底是福是禍？","createTime":"2017-05-11T13:17:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-11T16:38:34.000Z","uid":42243,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0b3117c3099fdbb2bb9441c42aa911c8445feb34","tid":239170,"uid":42243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T13:17:10.000Z","msg":"小弟係2017年DSE應屆考生，今日係圓玄三中考英文oral，同組有2女1男。而題型係debate。<br />\n<br />\n一開波，考生A就直接講個人立場，我就心唸：點解debate會有立場？跟住我就想睇定D先，點_知，<br />\n考生B：I Argree with you.........<br />\n我：.......？<br />\n考生B講_完<br />\n考生D: yes，you are right&hellip;&hellip;(認同立場)<br />\n呢個時候，我就知道，金翅仆街鳥<br />\n我：其實我地唔應該講個人立場，因為呢個係debate<br />\n考生A: (๑&deg;⌓&deg;๑).......唔好意思啊，我地而家係個gp到，所以應該講stance<br />\n我：.......<br />\n跟住我就自己講曬題目正反兩面，同埋move on topic，而過程中，另外三位考生不聽講個人立場，而且......<br />\n<br />\n_你老_佢地竟然最後達成共識，跟住問我ar唔argree，而呢刻，考官望住我的眼神係，憐憫，痛惜，定係嘲笑？我唔知，我真係唔知，我只知道，呢一刻，天灰了<br />\n<br />\n因為已經差唔多8點鐘<br />\n<br />\n個人問答尚算順利，考完出到考室，我同考生A講：其實debate唔洗個人立場，而係要講正反<br />\n考生A:下？點解啊？題目寫our group 喔，點解唔講得個人立場？<br />\n我：你自己翻去問老師啦<br />\n<br />\n小弟一袖清風地離去，路上亦聽見考生A一路大聲叫罵和堅持己見，因為有group，所以有stance，身邊友人亦不停附和。<br />\n<br />\n此時，無數名言在小弟腦海經過，如下：<br />\n<br />\n1：大千世界，無奇不有。<br />\n2：女人的確神秘莫測<br />\n<br />\n    &mdash;是福不是禍，是禍躲不過&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n終於明白，眾人皆醉我獨醒係咩感覺。<br />\n<br />\n多謝各位，不吐不快，若有錯誤，還望指正。<br />\n                         <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"339be350af5b8eb9a86b70479ace9488dd796a2f","tid":239170,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T13:18:56.000Z","msg":"出年再考過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50b77e0c7a421fccf580c5461dcfdea2240467e1","tid":239170,"uid":42243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T13:19:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>出年再考過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"383bc0cc9b52bbff72dc2acfb49fcd7ab24e5e67","tid":239170,"uid":42243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T13:21:12.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a41f630374628483576d3ca6e3bba16c8e8cb1e","tid":239170,"uid":41742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T13:21:18.000Z","msg":"會唔會係你睇錯題目？"},{"pid":"7a6edecffa399197b8933222fec023888f70c58e","tid":239170,"uid":42243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T13:21:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56752b578296f2e49165949c1e754ff2554aa079","tid":239170,"uid":42243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T13:21:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會唔會係你睇錯題目？</blockquote><br />\ndebate印撚住<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53bcd00573ac1d8377c33550fca2502a63e8476d","tid":239170,"uid":42243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T13:23:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"014ea66257ce236c5ad864f70bb04beac4b0dcf1","tid":239170,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T13:24:12.000Z","msg":"題目得一個字debate?如果係，恭喜您，下年考過啦，你英文程度太高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1ae41b0a5586224ead9c9419103b6ea5892e4c6","tid":239170,"uid":42243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T13:26:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>題目得一個字debate?如果係，恭喜您，下年考過啦，你英文程度太高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z992eW4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz992eW4.jpg&h=34